title: Zelenskyy accuses Putin of ‘delay tactics’ to stall Ukraine-Russia peace talks - Europe live
summary_full: Ukrainian president expresses growing frustration with Russia and the US over lack of progress on a deal Meanwhile, Ukraine said it successfully hit a Russian oil depot in the western region of Pskov, causing explosions and a fire, an official from Ukraine’s SBU security service.“The destruction of oil depots directly affects the enemy’s ability to conduct combat operations, advance and move staff reserves. Such operations are part of a systematic weakening of Russia’s military potential,” the official told Reuters. Continue reading...
